article.description: — David Collins posted 18 points and nine rebounds as South Florida defeated Stetson 73-62 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Collins scores 18 to lift South Florida past Stetson 73-62
article.linkText: Collins scores 18 to lift South Florida past Stetson 73-62
article.story: TAMPA, Fla. -- — David Collins posted 18 points and nine rebounds as South Florida defeated Stetson 73-62 on Tuesday. Collins made 8 of 10 shots. Justin Brown had 14 points for South Florida (3-2). Alexis Yetna added 13 points and eight rebounds, and Caleb Murphy had 12 points and six assists. Rob Perry had 15 points for the Hatters (0-4). Chase Johnston added 13 points and seven rebounds, and Mahamadou Diawara had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
